WEBVTT

00:05.728 --> 00:08.463
(theme music playing)

00:08.548 --> 00:11.966
This week on VICE, Boko
Haram's campaign of terror

00:12.102 --> 00:14.051
spreads across Africa.

00:14.137 --> 00:15.887
(men shouting)

00:20.643 --> 00:22.810
Behind me is a compound

00:22.946 --> 00:25.062
which two days ago was the site

00:25.148 --> 00:26.981
of a suicide attack.

00:27.066 --> 00:29.317
And then, advances
with our genetic code

00:29.452 --> 00:33.287
are changing the future
of human evolution.

00:33.373 --> 00:35.823
We're at the National Resource
Center for Mutant Mice.

00:35.959 --> 00:39.160
<i>They're editing</i>
<i>the mouse embryos right here.</i>

00:39.295 --> 00:41.045
The couple wants
a baby with blue eyes.

00:41.164 --> 00:42.663
<i>They said, "Can we get a boy,</i>

00:42.749 --> 00:44.632
<i>and can the boy have</i>
<i>blue eyes?"</i>

00:50.590 --> 00:51.923
(gunshot)

00:56.179 --> 00:59.063
(crowd chanting)

00:59.183 --> 01:05.614
<font color="#ec14bd">Sync & corrections by honeybunny
www.addic7ed.com</font>

01:06.022 --> 01:08.489
The deadliest terror group
in the world today

01:08.575 --> 01:10.491
isn't ISIS or Al Qaeda.

01:10.577 --> 01:12.410
According to a recent report,

01:12.529 --> 01:15.696
it's the Nigerian
terrorist group Boko Haram.

01:15.832 --> 01:18.699
And even after six years
of war with the military,

01:18.835 --> 01:21.369
Boko Haram is as deadly as ever,

01:21.454 --> 01:23.287
finding new ways to implement

01:23.373 --> 01:25.790
their terror tactics
in the region.

